history.content: You develop a web app using ruby on rails. The design of ruby is similar to python, an interpreted language with an emphasis on readability. I dont think you don't have to learn it in advance, but if you want a head start I guess you could look over some documentation and get familiar with ruby and ruby on rails, as well as HTML/CSS/JavaScript
